{"tid":1503383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「一個人的選舉」 澳门新特首-賀一誠","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T19:14:02.000Z","uid":148002,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"77f396f1bcc1bda155b2f16e9ad2ff6e3cfcf3d0","tid":1503383,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEPSX10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEPSX10.jpg&h=2fad5846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門第5屆行政長官選舉今日舉行，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>僅有澳門立法會前主席賀一誠作為唯一候選人。</strong></span></span>選舉將於早上10時舉行，由399名選委投票決定是否「信任」賀擔任特首。賀參選時曾稱當選後會考慮與本港銜接引渡罪犯事宜，近月亦不點名批評本港《逃犯條例》修例風波令一國兩制「走樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賀一誠於選舉提名期，在共399名選委中，獲379名選委提名。由於參選人必須取得6分1選委提名，即至少獲66個提名方可「入閘」，餘下的20名選委不足以再產生有效提名，他因此成為今次選舉的唯一候選人。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選舉於早上10時正式開始，399名選委於約9時起陸續進場，由於只有1名候選人，選委將投「信任票」。翻查資料，過往多次澳門特首選舉，由2004年的第2屆起，均只有1名候選人，並獲9成以上選委支持高票當選，而1999年第1屆選舉，前特首何厚鏵也獲8成以上選票當選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賀早年曾經多次公開表示無意角逐特首寶座，但今年2月卻透露有意參選，之後先後辭任澳門全國人大代表、立法會主席及議員等公職，並於6月正式宣佈參選。澳門財政司司長梁維特曾是另一特首選戰大熱門，卻在賀決定參選後，公開表示不會參選。外界盛傳賀是中央屬意的特首人選，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但他公開否認獲中央欽點，稱自己基於服務澳門的強烈使命感才決定參選。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日澳门</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">明日香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求。缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2a6234054cea5b5507b77d4d5f0fa53940441c79","tid":1503383,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbcfe717a60fcb677970899a62f5bd63c11b2a4","tid":1503383,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c05540117fa967e487c2e5b8f8c35961519b17","tid":1503383,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2e4d95ba25fbc166d6ba267e70fb0e97022cd2","tid":1503383,"uid":148002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"澳門人仲可以做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bf8b7c62eef9894b992cb79de55008b532c925","tid":1503383,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:24:38.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b49ad6315af9dd1507ac36e8cc67dab65eb74675","tid":1503383,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4bf8b7c62eef9894b992cb79de55008b532c925","tid":150